@host = http://localhost:5080

### Normal reading — should classify as Normal/Low
POST {{host}}/api/readings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sensorId": 101,
  "temperature": 24,
  "humidity": 45,
  "co2Level": 600
}

### Warning reading — high CO2 (>=1000) should classify as Warning/Medium
POST {{host}}/api/readings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sensorId": 102,
  "temperature": 25,
  "humidity": 50,
  "co2Level": 1200
}

### Fire reading — high temp (>=60) and danger CO2 (>=2000) should classify as Fire/High
POST {{host}}/api/readings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sensorId": 101,
  "temperature": 65,
  "humidity": 15,
  "co2Level": 2500
}

### Get latest 50 readings with their predictions
GET {{host}}/api/readings
